- **Modify:** `crates/muxer/src/stream_fetcher.rs`
- **Reference:** `crates/api/src/routes/stream.rs` lines 211-273 (chunked_stream fn)
- **Reference:** `crates/proxy/src/client.rs` (Range struct, ProxyClient)

